        <back>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1 b2">
                <p>Psalm 118:19, with "several discrepancies from the text redacted in … the
                    Septuagint." <lb/>"The serif … is more typical of the Late Roman period and may point to an even
                    earlier date, in the first half of the fifth century."<lb/>"The text shows several misspellings, typical of the period, most of which should
                    rather be described as phonetic spellings …"<lb/>The function of this verse at the entrance of churches was "definition of the
                    sacred space and separation between the sacred and the profane."</p>
            </div>
